options(repr.plot.width=10, repr.plot.height=3)
lab_groups <- c("low_clust_id", "high_clust_id", "lib_id") 
ggs <- lapply(lab_groups, function(lab) {
    g <- plot_scatter_discrete(meta_info, "tSNE_1", "tSNE_2", lab, 
                                cust_col=custom_colors(sample_name, lab)) + 
          ggtitle(lab)
    return(g)
})
grid.arrange(grobs=ggs, nrow = 1)
tsne_range <- list(x=layer_scales(ggs[[1]])$x$range$range, 
                   y=layer_scales(ggs[[1]])$y$range$range)

In [7]:
lab_type = "major_types"
meta_info[lab_type] <- load_cell_annotation(sample_name, meta_info, lab_type)
cell_sel <- meta_info[[lab_type]] %in% c("ATII", "Basal", "Club")
lab_type <- "major_types_3"
meta_info[lab_type] <- meta_info[["major_types"]]
meta_info[!cell_sel, lab_type] <- "Other"
lab_type <- "major_types_4"
basal_class <- load_cell_annotation(sample_name,  meta_info, "basal_1_vs_2")
meta_info[lab_type] <- meta_info[["major_types_3"]]
basal_sel <- basal_class != "Other"
meta_info[basal_sel, lab_type] <- basal_class[basal_sel]

label_type <- "major_types_3"
output_width <- 2.4
output_height <- 1.9
gene_markers <- c('SFTPC', 'KRT5', 'SCGB1A1')
plain_plts <- lapply(gene_markers, function(gene) {
    suppressMessages(manuscript_feat_plots(gene, label_type, meta_info, gex_dat_log, save=FALSE)) 
})
options(repr.plot.width=output_width*length(gene_markers), repr.plot.height=output_height)
grid.arrange(grobs=plain_plts, nrow = 1)
